    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">This ontology describes the findings from a project to create a reference data set for the PMD (Plattform Material Digital). It's intended to serve as a basis for developing and testing semantic web technology applications in the MSE domain. It uses the PMDco and the application ontology TTO.</rdfs:comment>
